title: Ibiza, Ibiza
content:
Ibiza, Ibiza is a 1986 Welsh comedy television film which aired on Welsh-language channel S4C.[1] It was directed by Ronw Protheroe and stars Caryl Parry Jones, Siw Hughes, Emyr Wyn [cy], and Huw Chiswell [cy].[2] It covers the stories of three women as they go on holiday to the island of Ibiza.
